From the beginning of August till the end of September, a remarkable mass departure of Italians from North to Center and South took place, with a sensible delay with respect to previous years and with a remarkable increment of internal travelling toward the Southern seas or mountains. Indeed, a statistical analysis reported in September 2020 by ENIT (the Italian National Agency for Tourism) shows that almost 24 millions of Italian went to Center-South for their holidays [19]. For this reason, as of July 20 we impose changes to the coefficients \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
